To be entirely serious and not autistic at all I think of anthros as being in a size range where they can be smaller than typical human, or larger, but not so much so that they are unable to use human-sized furniture and tools without too much difficulty. A certain 20th Century science fiction author wrote about a future in which humans had created genetically engineered human-animal hybrids as entertainers and slaves, denied all rights and legally subhuman. In one stories a character mentions that none of the "underpeople" is permitted to live if they are more than twice the size of a human, or less than half.
